terminator notes
ctrl-shift-o: split screen horizontally
ctrl-shift-p: focus on previous view
ctrl-shift-n: focus on next view
ctrl-shift-w: close the view where the focus is on
ctrl-shift-q: exit terminator
ctrl-shift-x: enlarge the active window

hide/show scroll bar A: ctrl-shift-s
search for a keyword- ctrl+shift+f
move to the above terminal - alt+up_arrow_key

increase front size: ctrl+(+)
decrease font size: ctrl+()
reset terminal size: ctrl+shift+r

group all terminal into one: super+g
remove all the terminal grouping: super+shift+t

note: super is a key with the 'logo' on the left CTRL side

